Whatever language you may speak, the staff
can help you with whatever questions you might have.

00:04:18.424 --> 00:04:22.580
I just think that the overall teaching here is pretty good.

00:04:22.795 --> 00:04:28.534
Always believe in your own goals and abilities and come to Akamonkai to achieve success.

00:04:28.534 --> 00:04:33.439
Together we can spread our wings and move 
forward not just in Japan but to the world.

